xxl.core.predicates

Interface MetaDataPredicate<P,M>

  • Type Parameters:
    P - the type of the predicate's parameters.
    M - the type of the meta data provided by this predicate.
    All Superinterfaces:
    MetaDataProvider<M>, Predicate<P>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractMetaDataPredicate, LeftBind, PredicateMetaDataPredicate, RightBind

    public interface MetaDataPredicate<P,M>
extends Predicate<P>, MetaDataProvider<M>
    A marker interface for predicates providing metadata.
